rnem\u00a0<strong>Volkswagen AG<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/kompletni-diagnostika-vaseho-vozu\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"Geometrie vozidla\" href=\"\/geometrie-vozidla\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/geometrie-s-1.jpg\" alt=\"Geometrie vozidla\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"caption caption__portfolio\">\n<h3><a href=\"\/geometrie-vozidla\">Geometrie vozidla<\/a><\/h3>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">K se\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed geometrie vozidla pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1me origin\u00e1ln\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed s technologi\u00ed\u00a03D.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/geometrie-vozidla\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"Diagnostika podvozku\" href=\"\/diagnostika-podvozku\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/podvozek-s.jpg\" alt=\"Diagnostika podvozku\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"caption caption__portfolio\">\n<h3><a href=\"\/diagnostika-podvozku\">Diagnostika podvozku<\/a><\/h3>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">Test tlumi\u010d\u016f, brzdov\u00e9ho syst\u00e9mu ( v\u010detn\u011b elektrick\u00e9 parkovac\u00ed brzdy ), detekce v\u016fl\u00ed obou n\u00e1prav.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/diagnostika-podvozku\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"Se\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed sv\u011btlomet\u016f\" href=\"\/serizeni-svetlometu\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/svetlomety.jpg\" alt=\"Se\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed sv\u011btlomet\u016f\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"caption caption__portfolio\">\n<h3><a href=\"\/serizeni-svetlometu\">Se\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed sv\u011btlomet\u016f<\/a><\/h3>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">Se\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed a kalibrace sv\u011btlomet\u016f (v\u010detn\u011b Led, HD Matrix Led-Laser ).<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/serizeni-svetlometu\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"P\u0158\u00cdPRAVA A REALIZACE STK\" href=\"\/priprava-a-realizace-stk\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/autoservis-thumb-rozcestnik.jpg\" alt=\"P\u0158\u00cdPRAVA A REALIZACE STKA\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"caption caption__portfolio\">\n<h3><a href=\"\/priprava-a-realizace-stk\/\">P\u0158\u00cdPRAVA A REALIZACE STK<\/a><\/h3>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">Zkontrolujeme a p\u0159iprav\u00edme v\u00e1\u0161 automobil p\u0159ed absolvov\u00e1n\u00edm st\u00e1tn\u00ed technick\u00e9 kontroly, nebo ji celou vy\u0159\u00edd\u00edme za v\u00e1s.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/priprava-a-realizace-stk\/\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"OPRAVY A PLN\u011aN\u00cd KLIMATIZAC\u00cd\" href=\"\/opravy-diagnostika-plneni-klimatizaci\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/klimatizace-s.jpg\" alt=\"OPRAVY A PLN\u011aN\u00cd KLIMATIZAC\u00cd\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"caption caption__portfolio\">\n<h3><a href=\"\/opravy-diagnostika-plneni-klimatizaci\/\">OPRAVY, PLN\u011aN\u00cd, \u010cI\u0160T\u011aN\u00cd\u00a0 KLIMATIZACE<\/a><\/h3>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">Dopln\u00edme chladivo do klimatizace, odhal\u00edme p\u0159\u00ed\u010dinu jej\u00edho \u0161patn\u00e9ho fungov\u00e1n\u00ed a p\u0159\u00edpadnou z\u00e1vadu odstran\u00edme.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/opravy-diagnostika-plneni-klimatizaci\/\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"PRODEJ A MONT\u00c1\u017d D\u00cdL\u016e A AUTODOPL\u0147K\u016e\" href=\"\/prodej-a-montaz-dilu-a-autodoplnku\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/dily-s.jpg\" alt=\"PRODEJ A MONT\u00c1\u017d D\u00cdL\u016e A AUTODOPL\u0147K\u016e\" \/><br \/>\n<\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"caption caption__portfolio\">\n<h3><a href=\"\/prodej-a-montaz-dilu-a-autodoplnku\/\">PRODEJ A MONT\u00c1\u017d D\u00cdL\u016e A AUTODOPL\u0147K\u016e<\/a><\/h3>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">Na objedn\u00e1vku zajist\u00edme v\u00e1mi po\u017eadovan\u00e9 n\u00e1hradn\u00ed d\u00edly nebo dopl\u0148ky. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b z\u00e1jmu provedeme tak\u00e9 jejich odbornou mont\u00e1\u017e.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" href=\"\/prodej-a-montaz-dilu-a-autodoplnku\/\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"portfolio_item isotope-item\">\n<div class=\"portfolio_item_holder\">\n<figure class=\"thumbnail thumbnail__portfolio\"><a class=\"image-wrap\" title=\"ZABEZPE\u010cEN\u00cd AUTA\" href=\"\/zabezpeceni-auta\"><br \/>\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/zabezpeceni-auta-rozce